609d3aba1eba65c45660ecca0891298cc5e07","tid":967690,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T21:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eedb3a90d61f8b507e42bf7c0fe81f10f106106","tid":967690,"uid":111398,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T17:14:27.000Z","msg":"以為自己開post<br />\n以前住hall特登買左隻靚杯用，到冇再住就拎返返黎用<br />\n屋企通常都有幾隻杯喺枱大家是但拎黎用<br />\n到我隻杯出現，屌，個個都淨係用我嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次忍唔住叫佢地唔好再用，明明大把杯係都要用我嗰隻<br />\n點知仲俾人話返我轉頭，自私又剩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩又俾人用左喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己鐘意既杯就咁變左做公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035f1da0981da3dc137e038351937b04f2d26259","tid":967690,"uid":54761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T17:18:48.000Z","msg":"同女友用同一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f902587c00fd05c369276a8f1ec96e9d3f23f6b3","tid":967690,"uid":15800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T17:43:24.000Z","msg":"唔係話嫌棄，但一人一隻有咩問題，又衛生啲<br />\n屋企人又話我自私，又話用完洗返咪得<br />\n<br />\n我啲杯有啲係古董，有啲雖然好平但係限量版，買唔返 <br />\n而且我自己係好錫杯，洗嗰時會慢慢用手捽，佢地就至鐘意用百潔布起勢捽，花Q曬<br />\n講左好多次都仲係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我心諗，牙杯又唔見你地share<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45711487c0fdf26012fe0b3ed0e2e4d954353fee","tid":967690,"uid":45105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T18:43:27.000Z","msg":"餐廳呢"},{"pid":"557981757fa6375b2b36698c9a6eaa5e3048314a","tid":967690,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6eedb3a90d61f8b507e42bf7c0fe81f10f106106","tid":967690,"uid":111398,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T17:14:27.000Z","msg":"以為自己開post<br />\n以前住hal